*CELEC Club Registration System*

A web application that lets students register to join the CELEC Club at USTHB.
Built using Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.

*STRUCTURE*

registration
        registration-backend    
  app.js
  package.json
  .env
  config/database.js
  models/userModel.js
  middlewares/validation.js
  controllers/controller.js
  routes/userRoutes.js

        registration-frontend

 style.css
 script.js
 logo.png



## How to Run It

cd registration-backend
node app.js 



